Package com.nathcat.peoplecat_server

Interface IPacketHandler

public interface IPacketHandler
Provides methods which can be implemented and used to handle packet types.

    • handle

      default Packet[] handle(ConnectionHandler handler, Packet[] packets)
      Handle a packet sequence by determining which handler method to pass it to. Uses the type of the first packet in the sequence to determine the appropriate handler method.
      Parameters:
      handler - The ConnectionHandler handling the connection
      packets - The packet sequence
      Returns:
      The resulting response packet sequence
